      <description>&lt;p&gt;⭐ El Kitab&amp;rsquo;ın bir yüzü: Kainat &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/33/72&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;33-72&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
⭐ Rabbimiz El-Kitab&amp;rsquo;ı; Rahim&amp;rsquo;de ilk gelişen organımıza(kalbimize) fıtrat olarak yazdı. &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/55/2&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;55-2&lt;/a&gt;
 &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/30/30&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;30-30&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
⭐ &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/2/213&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;2-213&lt;/a&gt;

İnsanlar bir tek topluluktu&amp;hellip;&lt;br&gt;
Sonra; anlaşmazlığa düştükleri konularda hükmetmeleri için El-Kitab&amp;rsquo;ı El-Hak ile indirdi&amp;hellip;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📌 &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/1/1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;1-1:&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
💎 İle s(e)m(a) Allah, El-Rahman, El-Rahim&lt;br&gt;
🔑 s(e)m(a): yükselten &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/11/41&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;11-41&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Allah: Ell-Hu(O) &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/112/1&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;112-1&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Rahman: Çok merhametli &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/19/75&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;19-75&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Rahim: Merhametini tecelli ettiren &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/39/53&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;39-53&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔎 &lt;a href=&#34;https://19.nakil.org/besmele&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Besmele-19&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;📌 &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/1/2&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;1-2:&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
💎 El-Hamd Allah için, Rabbidir, El-Alimler&amp;rsquo;in.&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Hamd: sorumluluk, hakkını vermek &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/9/112&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;9/112&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Rab: Öğrenmeyi öğreten &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/2/124&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;2-124&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔑 Alim: Bilen, emin olan &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/2/26&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;2-26&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
İçindeki alemi keşfeden &lt;a href=&#34;https://acikkuran.com/26/24&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;26-24&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;br&gt;
🔎 &lt;a href=&#34;https://19.nakil.org/besmele&#34; target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;&gt;Açılış-19&lt;/a&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;</description>
